{
  "texts": [
    "Two researchers then conducted title/abstract screening, with the first researcher coding either 'yes', 'no' or 'unsure' for inclusion, and the second researcher then reviewing all entries judged 'unsure' to decide inclusion.",
    "At this stage, we also recorded the aspects of Open Science (OA, OFD, etc.)",
    "to which the included studies were most relevant.",
    "After this, 453 of 472 studies sought were retrieved for full-text screening.",
    "All reasonable efforts were made to obtain full-texts, including inter-library loan and emailing authors."
  ]
}